Description: This is the companion package for the book "Introduction to 
    Hierarchical Bayesian Modeling for Ecological Data" (Parent and Rivot, 2012)
    . The package contains the datasets used in the booked as well as some
    helper functions for rstan and rjags. The analysis of the datasets are 
    provided as vignette.
